Cc: security@postgresql.org
Subject: Security Update Advisory

Dear PostgreSQL Community,

We are releasing security updates for all supported versions of PostgreSQL.
These updates address CVE-2026-0001 which affects all versions from 14 onwards.

Affected versions: 14.x, 15.x, 16.x, 17.x
Fixed versions: 14.15, 15.10, 16.6, 17.3

We recommend all users update their installations immediately.

For more details, see:
https://www.postgresql.org/support/security/

